title: Real Doner
typeOfFood: Lacto, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Turkish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Turkish restaurant on the outskirts of downtown. Some dishes are vegan by default, like the appetizers (minus yogurt or feta), falafel wrap/salad. On weekdays it offers a hot bar with veggie dishes. Patio and sdewalk area is removed from the street and enclosed by foliage.
